member.name: OVERLAPPED_ENTRY
member.summary: Contains the information returned by a call to theGetQueuedCompletionStatusExfunction.

member.name: OVERLAPPED_ENTRY.lpCompletionKey
member.summary: Receives the completion key value associated with the file handle whose I/O operation has completed. A completion key is a per-file key that is specified in a call toCreateIoCompletionPort.

member.name: OVERLAPPED_ENTRY.lpOverlapped
member.summary: Receives the address of the structure that was specified when the completed I/O operation was started.

member.name: OVERLAPPED_ENTRY.dwNumberOfBytesTransferred
member.summary: Receives the number of bytes transferred during the I/O operation that has completed.
